entry.title: Wagner Chief Says Russian Military Launched Strikes on His Camps
entry.content: Yevgeny Prigozhin accused Russia’s army of killing ‘an enormous amount’ of his troops with missile strikes and vowed to retaliate. Moscow denied the claims.

entry.title: U.S. Thinks Underwater Banging Noises Might Have Been Vessels Searching for Missing Submersible
entry.content: The investigation is starting to take shape, with one focus on the use of titanium and carbon fiber in the lost craft’s construction.
